name: Glamora Hill
address: Q9Q7+9H6, Pinggan, Kintamani, Bangli Regency, Bali 80652, Indonesia
review 1: The coffee place was swarming with flies and the area really had nothing attractive to it. No nice garden. True, they have a nice view but they could make an effort to make the grounds prettier, no?
review 2: beautiful spot to watch the sunrise
review 3: Good view, flat surface, quite spacious, good electricity. It has 2 toilet for males and females. I hope the owner can clean the toilet regularly and add a bathroom.
review 4: Nice view. Go early for free entry...
review 5: Everything was perfect - a clean place with a nice view apart from noisy kids singing with loud music not respecting other people who camped here. The reason was that nobody from the management stands by during the night  After a call to the management everything was fine again. We found the phone number on instagram. It would be nice if there is someone watching this place at night.

name: Batur Soul Bambo
address: Br Tabu Desa Songan Kintamani Bangli, Q9P9+5QQ, Songan A, Bangli, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80614, Indonesia
review 1: The view, overall is nice, but it's very cold. The triangle cabin is made of bamboo, so if you don't bring a thick jacket, then you will be freeze. The door of the cabin also made of wood and there is no key, the lock system still use a primitve way. So it's good for people who like it. But if you're not well prepared then you'll be freezing. The facility also nearly good, there is no hot tubs, there is kitchen that you can use, the owner also sell a firewood. But in my opinion, it's worth for the price. If you want to visit by motorcycle, i suggest you take detour, because the road is very steep.
